_title":"Taxi","original_language":"fr"},{"id":8367,"adult":false,"title":"Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves","video":false,"overview":"Nobleman crusader Robin of Locksley breaks out of a Jerusalem prison with the help of Moorish fellow prisoner Azeem and travels back home to England. But upon arrival he discovers his dead father in the ruins of his family estate, killed by the vicious sheriff of Nottingham, Robin and Azeem join forces with outlaws Little John and Will Scarlett to save the kingdom from the sheriff's villainy.","genre_ids":[28,12,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.4508,"vote_count":3498,"poster_path":"/hbRnWUNJkKKVN5mkcuC5ooqjE4e.jpg","release_date":"1991-06-14","vote_average":6.855,"backdrop_path":"/kuLk79GQq8WQb8fZxc6MtvIhPaC.jpg","original_title":"Robin Hood: Prince of Thieves","original_language":"en"},{"id":9003,"adult":false,"title":"Hellraiser","video":false,"overview":"A hedonistic man finds a mysterious puzzle box that summons a group of gruesome beings known as the Cenobites. These otherworldly entities open the doors to a dominion where pain and pleasure are indivisible.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.6132,"vote_count":2803,"poster_path":"/3Z0oPHyLnk3Vx6ZMC1MiVwIrKhO.jpg","release_date":"1987-09-11","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/j4irvwRLITgGr6vcP8NIKCUA67y.jpg","original_title":"Hellraiser","original_language":"en"},{"id":429351,"adult":false,"title":"12 Strong","video":false,"overview":"A team of special forces head into Afghanistan in the aftermath of the September 11th attacks in an attempt to dismantle the Taliban.","genre_ids":[10752,18,28,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.0125,"vote_count":3142,"poster_path":"/37Qwani2g0jVPU7N4OkkTZ7aERz.jpg","release_date":"2018-01-18","vote_average":6.35,"backdrop_path":"/x5EUEv1N9g4BCX9GQXKvv3nqMVo.jpg","original_title":"12 Strong","original_language":"en"},{"id":10501,"adult":false,"title":"The Road to El Dorado","video":false,"overview":"Stowing away after