9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"4x4 | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Buenos Aires, Argentina. A luxurious van is parked on the sidewalk. A man enters with the purpose of stealing whatever he can find, but when he wants to leave, he cannot. The doors do not open, the control panel does not respond: the van has become an armored box and he is trapped like a mouse."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148347/4x4"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"4x4"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Buenos Aires, Argentina. A luxurious van is parked on the sidewalk. A man enters with the purpose of stealing whatever he can find, but when he wants to leave, he cannot. The doors do not open, the control panel does not respond: the van has become an armored box and he is trapped like a mouse."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148347/4x4"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4o3Wr0zrYot5Q3rVS7c3YlFOpYJ.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"4x4"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Buenos Aires, Argentina. A luxurious van is parked on the sidewalk. A man enters with the purpose of stealing whatever he can find, but when he wants to leave, he cannot. The doors do not open, the control panel does not respond: the van has become an armored box and he is trapped like a mouse."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4o3Wr0zrYot5Q3rVS7c3YlFOpYJ.jpg"}],["$"